rows.name: I took it with me earlier, but...

rows.label: bf11290100_0020
rows.name:
after all, I'd be happy if
Mother would use it forever...

rows.label: bf11290100_0040
rows.name:
Hoh? So the slut finally croaked.
A real shame, I was quite fond of her.

rows.label: bf11290100_0060
rows.name:
Heh. So you've learned to take
a proper stance, haven't you...

rows.label: bf11290100_0070
rows.name:
For a little girl who used to shake so bad
she looked like she'd piss her pants.
